process-name: string
in path

200 OK
vrfs_schema

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

VRF - Retrieve

Retrieve operation of resource: vrf

process-name: string
in path

ID of process-name

vrf-name: string
in path

ID of vrf-name

200 OK
vrf_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error
